I"V<p>A web app to replace the announcer when playing The Resistance: Avalon.</p>

<h2 id="instructions">Instructions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Use the button in the bottom left to select the number of players.</li>
  <li>Select the desired roles.</li>
  <li>Distribute and privately view role cards.</li>
  <li>Press play to begin narration.</li>
</ol>
